---

<section class="lifecycle-section">
  <h2 class="section-title">How AIOS Works</h2>
  <p class="section-subtitle">A repeatable loop from idea to reviewed implementation.</p>
  <div class="lifecycle-steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">1</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Setup</h3>
        <p>Install AIOS, create or adopt a project.</p>
        <code>aios init my-project</code>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">2</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Product Vision</h3>
        <p>Agent interviews you and fills the vision doc.</p>
        <code>product-discovery</code>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">3</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>PRD</h3>
        <p>Generate a PRD with testable acceptance criteria.</p>
        <code>prd-generator</code>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">4</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Architecture</h3>
        <p>Design architecture and record decisions.</p>
        <code>architecture-design</code>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">5</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Tasks</h3>
        <p>Break work into small, verifiable tasks.</p>
        <code>task-breakdown</code>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">6</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Implement</h3>
        <p>Build one task at a time with tests.</p>
        <code>task-implementation</code>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">7</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Review</h3>
        <p>Review the diff against acceptance criteria.</p>
        <code>code-review</code>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-number">8</div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <h3>Next</h3>
        <p>Ask what to do next, then repeat from step 5.</p>
        <code>aios next</code>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .lifecycle-section {
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  .section-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }
  .lifecycle-steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.25rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-card-start), var(--color-card-end));
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 1rem;
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  .step:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-border-strong);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .step-number {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--color-accent-soft);
    color: var(--color-accent-2);
    border-radius: 50%;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }
  .step-content h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
  }
  .step-content p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .step-content code {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    background: var(--color-code-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    color: var(--color-accent-2);
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, monospace;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .lifecycle-steps {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .lifecycle-steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
